                "invention-title": [
                    "Carbon capture coupling hydrogen production method and device",
                    "碳捕集耦合制氢的方法及装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a method and a device for carbon capture coupling hydrogen production. The method comprises the following steps: capturing low-concentration CO2 by using an alkali metal hydroxide solution to obtain a low-concentration CO2 absorption liquid, and capturing high-concentration CO2 by using a first part of the low-concentration CO2 absorption liquid to obtain a high-concentration CO2 absorption liquid; and carrying out electrolysis by taking the second part of low-concentration CO2 absorption liquid as a catholyte, taking the high-concentration CO2 absorption liquid as an anolyte and taking a non-ionic diaphragm as a diaphragm. According to the method disclosed by the invention, the capture of the CO2 in a wide concentration range can be realized, the non-ionic diaphragm is used for electrolysis to realize regeneration of the absorption liquid and coupled hydrogen production, the capture cost of the CO2 in the wide concentration range can be reduced, additional products of H2 and O2 are obtained, and meanwhile, the hydrogen production cost is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种碳捕集耦合制氢的方法及装置。该方法包括：利用碱金属氢氧化物溶液捕集低浓度CO2，得到低浓度CO2吸收液，利用第一部分低浓度CO2吸收液捕集高浓度CO2，得到高浓度CO2吸收液；将第二部分低浓度CO2吸收液作为阴极液，将高浓度CO2吸收液作为阳极液，将非离子型隔膜作为隔膜，进行电解。本发明的方法可以实现宽浓度范围CO2的捕集，使用非离子型隔膜进行电解实现吸收液的再生并耦合制氢，可以降低宽浓度范围CO2捕集成本，并得到H2、O2的附加产品，同时降低了制氢成本。"
                }
            ]
